        textEn: 'Before a country can become a member of the Council of Europe, it must recognize its citizens\' personal and political civil liberties. The purpose of the Council of Europe is to ensure close cooperation between its member states in a wide range of political areas. Russia was suspended from the Council of Europe after the attack on Ukraine in 2022.',
